title: Neff North vs. South teaser
description: Get ready for one of the sickest video edit contests ever. Neff teamed up with TransWorld Skateboarding to bring you North vs. South. We pitted 8 of the best skate shop teams against each other in a video edit contest with the winner receiving a feature in an upcoming TWS. Watch the full edits and vote here bit.ly/NeffNorthvsSouth
